
# sequenceDiagram
#     participant User
#     participant DjangoView as Django View/Admin
#     participant WorkOrder
#     participant RepairStep
#     participant Inspection
#     participant ActivityLog

#     User->>DjangoView: Submit request to close Work Order
#     DjangoView->>WorkOrder: Update status = CLOSED, set closed_at
#     DjangoView->>WorkOrder: full_clean()

#     WorkOrder->>RepairStep: Check for pending steps
#     RepairStep-->>WorkOrder: Return step statuses

#     WorkOrder->>Inspection: Check for PASS inspection
#     Inspection-->>WorkOrder: Return inspection results

#     alt All steps DONE and PASS inspection exists
#         WorkOrder->>WorkOrder: save()
#         WorkOrder->>ActivityLog: Create WO_CLOSED event
#         ActivityLog-->>WorkOrder: Log saved
#         WorkOrder-->>DjangoView: Save successful
#         DjangoView-->>User: Work Order closed successfully
#     else Validation fails
#         WorkOrder-->>DjangoView: Raise ValidationError
#         DjangoView-->>User: Close rejected with error message
#     (end)